nscrypt-doh-client/id1330471557?mt=8</a><br />\n<br />\n裝後可以選擇 adguard 做 DNS server <br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/hoLnuNh.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FhoLnuNh.png&h=8cd148ba&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n進階 menu 又可以有 custom blocklist, 用黎 block 返 <a href=\"http://oscp.apple.com\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Foscp.apple.com&d=ayxGCzeFtYLQTdJ4vPfzY%2F9tTpBMMlQtk6PgfkTA9U8%3D&h=3519fcf0\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">oscp.apple.com</a><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/CCB9Ud9.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FCCB9Ud9.png&h=5ef31a8d&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n咁就禮成 <img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/bang.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"10b5563b11609e9b8880caa14c408b93b48a7ae4","tid":908441,"uid":189021,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-19T14:38:25.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n竟然唔係膠post"},{"pid":"638eb697440e62e0f59ae13923cdacd2ac737bc7","tid":908441,"uid":19285,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-11-19T15:53:35.000Z","msg":"我自己router 有得set vpn<br />\n係咪block <a href=\"http://上面apple.com\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2F%E4%B8%8A%E9%9D%A2apple.com&d=ayxGCzeFtYLQTdJ4vPfzY%2F9tTpBMMlQtk6PgfkTA9U8%3D&h=1e0c2402\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">上面apple.com</a> 果個link 就ok?<br />\n有冇block ads list 開心share??"},{"pid":"401c5568c34051933c2177053819d066f266c0c7","tid":908441,"uid":18044,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-19T16:19:39.000Z","msg":"即係有咩用<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f6d9cb1a82c5c168867d6dc6c3ad1bbfa5363913","tid":908441,"uid":123991,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"638eb697440e62e0f59ae13923cdacd2ac737bc7","tid":908441,"uid":19285,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-11-19T15:53:35.000Z"